  "planContent": "# 🏗️ Architecture Blueprint\n\n## App Overview\nA premium iPhone 18 Pro Max product landing page showcasing the device's flagship features through an immersive, high-performance single-page experience. The page delivers a cinematic hero sequence, modular feature grid with macro asset photography, and conversion-optimized call-to-action sections, all built with strict adherence to the provided Stitch design system and dark theme color palette.\n\n## Core Features\n- **Fixed Navigation Bar**: Logo, section links (Overview, Tech Specs, Compare), and prominent \"Buy\" button with blur backdrop and smooth transitions\n- **Hero Section with Animated Headline**: Full-viewport hero with fade-in animation, subheading, dual CTA buttons (Buy Now, Watch Film), and macro photography showcase\n- **Feature Bento Grid Layout**: Responsive 12-column grid showcasing five distinct feature cards (A18 Pro Chip, 100MP Camera, Zero-Edge Display, Grade 5 Titanium, and hardware showcase)\n- **Individual Feature Cards**: Each card contains headline, descriptive text, background imagery with hover zoom effects, and layered design elements\n- **A18 Pro Chip Component**: Large card with animated gradient blur effect and centered chip badge\n- **100MP Camera System Card**: Image reveal on hover with transform scaling\n- **Zero-Edge Display Card**: Phone frame illustration with gradient overlay\n- **Titanium Strength Card**: Full-width dual-content layout with texture imagery overlay\n- **Hardware Showcase Section**: Dark background section with large \"PRO MAX\" typography watermark, side-profile device image, and descriptive copy\n- **CTA Section**: Dual action buttons (Order Now, Compare Models) with pricing callout\n- **Footer**: Seven-column link structure with Store, Entertainment, Support, and About categories; copyright and legal links; responsive grid collapse\n- **Image Referrer Policy Compliance**: All images include referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" meta tag and attribute to prevent 403 errors from Google CDN\n- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first responsive adjustments from 375px to 1440px viewports with stacked single-column layouts on mobile\n\n## UI & Layout Strategy\n- **Layout Type**: Single-column stacked with CSS Grid bento feature section; full-width hero to footer flow\n- **Header**: Fixed 12px height navigation bar with semi-transparent dark background (#0e0e0e/60), backdrop blur effect, left logo section (iOS icon + \"iPhone 18 Pro Max\" text), center navigation links (hidden on mobile), right \"Buy\" button in primary color\n- **Main Content Area**:\n  - Hero section (min-height screen) with centered text content, fade-in animation on headline, dual CTA buttons (Buy Now, Watch Film), and 16:9 aspect ratio macro photography showcase below\n  - Feature grid section (py-32) using Tailwind 12-column responsive grid with 6px gap spacing\n  - Immersive hardware showcase section with dark background, centered headline/subheading, and device image with drop shadow\n  - Final CTA section (py-32) with dual buttons and pricing text\n- **Controls**:\n  - \"Buy\" button (primary, nav bar): px-4 py-1.5, rounded-full, text-xs, hover opacity-80, active scale-95\n  - \"Buy Now\" button (hero): bg-primary, px-8 py-4, rounded-full, text-lg font-bold, hover bg-primary-dim, active scale-95\n  - \"Watch the film\" link: text-primary, text-lg, underline hover, flex with play_circle icon\n  - \"Order Now\" button (CTA): bg-primary, px-12 py-5, rounded-full, text-xl, w-full md:w-auto, active scale-95\n  - \"Compare Models\" button (CTA): bg-surface-container, border border-outline-variant/10, px-12 py-5, rounded-full, text-xl, hover bg-surface-container-high\n- **Footer**: 7-column grid (responsive to 4 on md, 2 on sm) with category headers, link lists, copyright block, and legal links row\n- **Design System**: Strict Tailwind CSS utility classes; no custom CSS except for Material Symbols Outlined font and body min-height rule; extends custom color palette defined in tailwind.config\n- **Color Scheme**: \n  - Primary background: #0e0e0e (surface, background)\n  - Secondary dark: #131313 (surface-container-low, footer)\n  - Container: #191919 (surface-container)\n  - Text primary: #e5e5e5 (on-surface)\n  - Text secondary: #ababab (on-surface-variant)\n  - Accent: #c6c6c8 (primary, button backgrounds)\n  - Borders/dividers: #484848 (outline-variant), #262626 (surface-variant)\n  - Subtle accents: #757575 (outline), #1f1f1f (surface-container-high)\n- **Responsive Strategy**:\n  - Mobile (375px): Single-column layout; navigation links hidden (hidden md:flex); buttons full-width (w-full md:w-auto); text sizes scale down (text-[3.5rem] on mobile becomes text-[5rem] on md, text-[6.5rem] on lg); hero image full-width with padding; grid becomes 1 column (grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12)\n  - Desktop (1440px): Multi-column grid with 12-column spans (md:col-span-8, md:col-span-4); navigation links visible; buttons inline; text at full size; feature cards arranged in bento layout\n- **Animations & UX**:\n  - Hero headline: opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-out_forwards] (custom fade animation)\n  - Macro asset image: grayscale brightness-75 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000\n  - Camera card image: group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\n  - Titanium card image: group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-1000\n  - Button hover effects: hover:opacity-80, hover:bg-primary-dim, hover:scale-105 (camera card)\n  - All buttons active state: active:scale-95 duration-200\n  - Navigation links: hover:opacity-80 or hover:text-[#e5e5e5] with transition-opacity/colors\n  - Feature cards: overflow-hidden with relative positioning for image layering\n- **Touch Targets**: All buttons minimum 44px height (py-4 = 16px + padding, py-5 = 20px + padding); links have adequate padding; hover states provide visual feedback\n- **Accessibility**:\n  - Material Symbols Outlined icons with semantic role (e.g., play_circle for video, apple for logo)\n  - All images have alt text and data-alt attributes describing content\n  - Navigation links are semantic <a> tags with href attributes\n  - Button focus rings via active:scale-95 states (visual feedback); add focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary to all buttons\n  - Section landmarks: <nav>, <main>, <section>, <footer> semantic HTML\n  - Heading hierarchy: <h1> for hero, <h2> for section titles\n  - Color contrast: text-on-surface (#e5e5e5) on bg-surface (#0e0e0e) meets WCAG AA\n  - Footer links: clickable text with cursor-pointer class\n  - ARIA labels on icon-only elements: aria-label=\"Apple\" on logo icon\n\n## Data Model & State\n| Variable | Type | Default | Description |\n|----------|------|---------|-------------|\n| currentSection | String | \"overview\" | Tracks which top nav link is active for styling |\n| imageHoverState | Object | {} | Tracks hover state for each feature card image (used for group-hover effects) |\n| scrollPosition | Number | 0 | Current window scroll Y position (for potential parallax or lazy-load optimization) |\n| isMobileNav | Boolean | window.innerWidth < 768 | Tracks if viewport is mobile to conditionally render nav links |\n| cartItems | Array | [] | Future e-commerce integration; empty for landing page |\n| analytics | Object | {} | Stores page view, scroll depth, CTA click events for tracking |\n\n- **Persistence Strategy**: No data persistence required for landing page. All state is ephemeral and tied to user interactions (hover, scroll, navigation clicks). Use `window.scrollTo()` and CSS scroll-behavior for smooth navigation. No database calls needed.\n\n## Technical Stack & Libraries\n- **Required CDNs**:\n  - Tailwind CSS v3 with forms and container-queries plugins: `https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries`\n  - Google Fonts Inter (weights 300–800): `https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap`\n  - Material Symbols Outlined: `https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap`\n- **Allowed Libraries**: Tailwind CSS only (no external component libraries); Material Symbols for iconography; Google Fonts for typography\n- **APIs**: None (100% offline, static content)\n- **Images**: All sourced from Google CDN with referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" to comply with CORS policies\n\n## Implementation Steps\n1. **Set up HTML structure with doctype and meta tags**: Create `<!DOCTYPE html>`, add charset UTF-8, viewport meta (width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0), title \"iPhone 18 Pro Max\", and **critical meta tag `<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">` in `<head>` to prevent 403 errors on Google CDN images**. Add Tailwind CSS CDN script with plugins parameter, Google Fonts Inter and Material Symbols links.\n\n2. **Configure Tailwind dark theme and custom colors**: Insert `<script id=\"tailwind-config\">` block defining `darkMode: \"class\"` and extending theme colors with all 50+ custom color tokens (primary, surface, on-surface-variant, outline-variant, etc.). Add custom font family definitions (headline, body, label) all using Inter. Set border-radius defaults and extend config.\n\n3. **Create inline styles for global body and typography**: Add `<style>` block with `body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }`, Material Symbols font-variation-settings, text-shadow-premium utility class, no-scrollbar utility, and minimum body height rule (`min-height: max(884px, 100dvh)`).\n\n4. **Build fixed navigation bar**: Create `<nav class=\"fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#0e0e0e]/60 backdrop-blur-xl\">` with flex container (max-w-[1200px], mx-auto, px-6, h-12). Left section: iOS icon span + \"iPhone 18 Pro Max\" text (font-semibold, tracking-tight). Center: three links (Overview, Tech Specs, Compare) with hidden md:flex, opacity transitions on hover. Right: \"Buy\" button (bg-primary, text-on-primary, px-4 py-1.5, rounded-full, text-xs, hover:opacity-80, active:scale-95).\n\n5. **Implement hero section with animation**: Create `<section class=\"relative min-h-screen\">` with flex column, center items/justify. Add animated `<h1>` (text-[3.5rem] md:text-[5rem] lg:text-[6.5rem], font-bold, leading-[1.05], tracking-tighter, opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-out_forwards]). Add `<p>` subheading (text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem], text-on-surface-variant). Add dual CTA buttons: \"Buy Now\" (bg-primary, px-8 py-4, rounded-full, text-lg, hover:bg-primary-dim, active:scale-95) and \"Watch the film\" link (text-primary, flex items-center, play_circle icon). Add 16:9 aspect ratio image container (aspect-[16/9], max-w-6xl, mx-auto, rounded-xl, shadow-2xl) with grayscale brightness-75 image and hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000 and gradient overlay.\n\n6. **Build 12-column feature grid bento layout**: Create `<section class=\"py-32 px-6 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto\">` with `<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6\">`. Implement five feature cards as children: **(a) A18 Pro Chip (md:col-span-8)**: bg-surface-container, p-10, min-h-[500px], flex flex-col justify-between. Top section with \"Engineered for Intelligence\" label (text-primary, text-xs, uppercase, tracking-widest), h2 headline, and paragraph. Bottom: h-64 container with absolute w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 blur-[100px] glow effect, centered badge (w-48 h-48, bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-container to-surface-container-high, rounded-3xl, border, shadow-inner, flex items-center justify-center) with \"A18\" text (text-primary, font-black, text-4xl, italic).\n\n7. **Add camera, display, and titanium feature cards**: Create remaining four bento grid items: **(b) 100MP Camera (md:col-span-4)**: bg-surface-container-low, p-10, min-h-[500px], relative group, headline/text in z-10, absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 image with grayscale and group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700. **(c) Zero-Edge Display (md:col-span-4)**: bg-surface-container-high, p-10, min-h-[400px], headline, text, mt-auto card with h-1 gradient line and aspect-[9/16] phone frame. **(d) Titanium Strength (md:col-span-8)**: bg-surface-container, p-10, flex items-center justify-between, min-h-[400px], left content in max-w-sm z-10, right image overlay (absolute top-0 right-0 h-full w-1/2) with grayscale and group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-1000. Ensure all images include `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"` attribute.\n\n8. **Create immersive hardware showcase section**: Build `<section class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest py-32 overflow-hidden\">` with centered content (max-w-[1200px], mx-auto, px-6, flex flex-col items-center). Add centered h2 headline (text-[3rem] md:text-[4.5rem], font-bold, tracking-tight, mb-6) and subheading `<p>` (text-xl, text-on-surface-variant, max-w-2xl). Add relative h-[600px] container with absolute \"PRO MAX\" watermark text (text-[15rem], font-black, tracking-tighter, opacity-20, select-none, pointer-events-none) and device image (max-w-full, h-auto, max-h-[500px], object-contain, drop-shadow-[0_35px_35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)], z-10) with `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"`.\n\n9. **Build final CTA section**: Create `<section class=\"py-32 bg-surface text-center\">` with max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6. Add h2 headline (text-[2.5rem] md:text-[4rem], font-bold, text-on-surface, mb-8). Add flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 container with two buttons: (a) \"Order Now\" (bg-primary, text-on-primary, px-12 py-5, rounded-full, text-xl, font-bold, w-full md:w-auto, hover:bg-primary-dim, active:scale-95), (b) \"Compare Models\" (bg-surface-container, text-on-surface, border border-outline-variant/10, px-12 py-5, rounded-full, text-xl, w-full md:w-auto, hover:bg-surface-container-high, active:scale-95). Add `<p>` pricing text (mt-8, text-on-surface-variant).\n\n10. **Implement footer with seven-column layout**: Create `<footer class=\"bg-[#131313] py-12 px-6 border-t border-[#484848]/15\">` with max-w-[1200px] mx-auto. Add `<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-8 mb-12\">` with four sections: (a) Store (Mac, iPad, iPhone, Watch), (b) Entertainment (Apple One, Apple TV+, Apple Music, Arcade), (c) Support (iPhone Support, Apple Care, Community, Contact), (d) About Apple (paragraph text). Each section has category `<span>` header (text-[#e5e5e5], font-bold, text-[0.75rem]) and `<ul>` with links (text-[#ababab], text-[0.75rem], hover:underline, cursor-pointer). Add bottom `<div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-[#484848]/15\">` with copyright text and legal links row (flex gap-6, Privacy Policy, Terms of Use, Sales Policy, Legal).\n\n11. **Add accessibility attributes and ARIA labels**: Inject `aria-label=\"Apple Logo\"` on logo icon. Add `aria-label=\"Navigation\"` on `<nav>`. Add `aria-label=\"Main Content\"` on `<main>`. Add `role=\"contentinfo\"` on `<footer>`. Add focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary to all buttons. Verify heading hierarchy (h1 for hero, h2 for sections). Confirm all images have alt and data-alt attributes.\n\n12. **Optimize images and referrer policy compliance**: Ensure every `<img>` tag includes `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"` and alt text. Verify `<head>` includes `<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">`. Keep original Google CDN URLs unchanged. Test image load behavior in browser DevTools Network tab to confirm no 403 errors.\n\n13. **Test responsive breakpoints**: Validate layout at 375px (mobile portrait), 768px (tablet), and 1440px (desktop) using Chrome DevTools. Confirm: navigation links hidden on mobile (hidden md:flex), buttons full-width on mobile (w-full md:w-auto), text sizes scale correctly (text-[3.5rem] to text-[6.5rem] progression), grid columns collapse (grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12).\n\n14. **Implement and verify animations**: Test fade-in animation on hero h1 (opacity-0 animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-out_forwards]). Verify all hover:scale-105/110/125 transitions on images (duration-700 or duration-1000). Test button active:scale-95 states. Confirm smooth transitions on navigation links (transition-opacity, transition-colors).\n\n15. **Final polish and cross-browser testing**: Run page in Chrome, Firefox, Safari desktop and iOS Safari mobile. Verify: all images load without 403 errors, animations smooth, buttons clickable with adequate touch targets (44px minimum), text readable at all breakpoints, footer links functional, no console errors, scroll behavior smooth, color contrast accessible (WCAG AA).\n\n## Edge Cases & Error Handling\n- **Image Load Failures (403 Forbidden)**: Mitigation: Include `<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">` in `<head>` and `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"` on all `<img>` tags. If images still fail, provide fallback solid color backgrounds (e.g., bg-surface-container) or graceful degradation with transparent overlays. Do not cache in localStorage; let browser cache handle it.\n- **Empty Image Alt Text**: All images must have non-empty alt and data-alt attributes. Provide descriptive text (e.g., \"Close-up macro photography of brushed obsidian titanium texture\") for accessibility and SEO.\n- **Network Latency**: Page is static HTML/CSS/JS; no API calls. Images load asynchronously via <img> tags. Use loading=\"lazy\" on below-fold images (zero-edge display card, hardware showcase, footer) to defer rendering.\n- **Mobile Viewport Overflow**: Ensure all containers use max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 for consistent padding. Verify no horizontal scroll at 375px viewport (test with Chrome DevTools device emulation).\n- **Animation Performance**: Use transform and opacity for animations (GPU-accelerated); avoid animating layout properties. Tested duration values: fadeIn 1s, hover transforms 700ms–1000ms are smooth on average devices.\n- **Touch Target Size**: All buttons ≥ 44px tall (py-4 = 16px + padding, py-5 = 20px + padding). Spacing between clickable elements ≥ 6px (gap-6 used throughout). Test on actual mobile device or DevTools emulation.\n- **Browser Compatibility**: Tailwind CSS v3 supports all modern browsers (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge). Custom color tokens and backdrop-blur work in all modern browsers. Fallback for older browsers: page degrades gracefully with solid colors instead of gradients.\n- **Scroll Performance**: Use CSS scroll-behavior: smooth if needed. Avoid JavaScript scroll listeners; rely on native browser smooth scrolling. No infinite scroll or dynamic content loading; static page.\n- **Focus Management**: Users navigating via keyboard should see visible focus rings on all interactive elements (buttons, links). Add focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary to all buttons and `<a>` tags.\n- **Color Contrast Accessibility**: Primary text (#e5e5e5 on #0e0e0e) passes WCAG AA. Secondary text (#ababab on #0e0e0e) is borderline AA; ensure sufficient size (16px+) for readability.\n- **Missing Tailwind Classes**: Ensure all custom color tokens are defined in tailwind.config theme.extend.colors. If a class like `bg-surface-container` is undefined, the style silently fails; verify all color references exist in config.\n- **Footer Responsiveness**: At 375px, footer grid collapses to 2 columns (grid-cols-2). At 768px, becomes 4 columns (md:grid-cols-4). At 1024px+, 7 columns (lg:grid-cols-7). Test wrapping at all breakpoints.\n\n---\n\n**CRITICAL IMPLEMENTATION NOTES:**\n- **Referrer Policy**: The provided Stitch design already includes image URLs from Google CDN. To prevent 403 Forbidden errors, you MUST include `<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\">` in the `<head>` section and add `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"` attribute to every single `<img>` tag. Do not modify the image URLs themselves.\n- **Custom Tailwind Config**: The provided design includes an extensive custom color palette in `tailwind.config`. Every color token (e.g., `primary`, `surface-container-high`, `on-surface-variant`) must be defined in the theme.extend.colors section. Copy the entire colors object from the design source.\n- **Font Smoothing**: Maintain `-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased` on body for crisp text rendering on macOS.\n- **Material Symbols Font**: Ensure both Material Symbols Outlined CDN links are included (the design includes the link twice, which is harmless). Icons are rendered with `<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">icon_name</span>`.\n- **Animations**: The fade-in animation is custom and defined in the Tailwind config as `animate-[fadeIn_1s_ease-out_forwards]`. Define this as a keyframe if it's missing: `@keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }`.",
  "currentHTML": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"dark\" lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\"/>\n<meta name=\"referrer\" content=\"no-referrer\"/>\n<title>iPhone 18 Pro Max</title>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries\"></script>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<script id=\"tailwind-config\">\ntailwind.config = {\n  darkMode: \"class\",\n  theme: {\n    extend: {\n      colors: {\n        \"outline-variant\": \"#484848\",\n        \"on-surface-variant\": \"#ababab\",\n        \"secondary\": \"#9d9da2\",\n        \"tertiary-fixed\": \"#d3ceef\",\n        \"on-secondary-fixed\": \"#3e3f43\",\n        \"on-tertiary\": \"#504d68\",\n        \"on-error\": \"#490106\",\n        \"surface-container\": \"#191919\",\n        \"primary-container\": \"#454749\",\n        \"secondary-fixed\": \"#e3e2e7\",\n        \"tertiary\": \"#e1dcfd\",\n        \"surface-tint\": \"#c6c6c8\",\n        \"surface\": \"#0e0e0e\",\n        \"on-tertiary-container\": \"#47445f\",\n        \"surface-bright\": \"#2c2c2c\",\n        \"on-tertiary-fixed\": \"#34314b\",\n        \"primary-fixed-dim\": \"#d4d4d6\",\n        \"error-container\": \"#7f2927\",\n        \"background\": \"#0e0e0e\",\n        \"inverse-primary\": \"#5d5f61\",\n        \"primary-dim\": \"#b8b9bb\",\n        \"on-secondary\": \"#1f2024\",\n        \"surface-container-high\": \"#1f1f1f\",\n        \"on-primary\": \"#3e4042\",\n        \"on-primary-fixed\": \"#3e3f41\",\n        \"error-dim\": \"#bb5551\",\n        \"surface-variant\": \"#262626\",\n        \"secondary-fixed-dim\": \"#d4d4d9\",\n        \"primary-fixed\": \"#e2e2e4\",\n        \"on-primary-fixed-variant\": \"#5a5c5d\",\n        \"secondary-container\": \"#3a3b3f\",\n        \"on-secondary-container\": \"#bfbfc4\",\n        \"surface-container-highest\": \"#262626\",\n        \"on-tertiary-fixed-variant\": \"#504e69\",\n        \"tertiary-fixed-dim\": \"#c5c0e0\",\n        \"surface-container-lowest\": \"#000000\",\n        \"secondary-dim\": \"#9d9da2\",\n        \"on-background\": \"#e5e5e5\",\n        \"inverse-surface\": \"#f9f9f9\",\n        \"on-primary-container\": \"#d0d0d2\",\n        \"primary\": \"#c6c6c8\",\n        \"tertiary-dim\": \"#c5c0e0\",\n        \"on-error-container\": \"#ff9993\",\n        \"error\": \"#ee7d77\",\n        \"on-secondary-fixed-variant\": \"#5a5b60\",\n        \"surface-container-low\": \"#131313\",\n        \"tertiary-container\": \"#d3ceef\",\n        \"outline\": \"#757575\",\n        \"inverse-on-surface\": \"#555555\",\n        \"on-surface\": \"#e5e5e5\",\n        \"surface-dim\": \"#0e0e0e\"\n      },\n      fontFamily: {\n        \"headline\": [\"Inter\"],\n        \"body\": [\"Inter\"],\n        \"label\": [\"Inter\"]\n      },\n      borderRadius: {\n        \"DEFAULT\": \"0.25rem\",\n        \"lg\": \"0.5rem\",\n        \"xl\": \"0.75rem\",\n        \"full\": \"9999px\"\n      },\n      animation: {\n        fadeIn: \"fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards\"\n      },\n      keyframes: {\n        fadeIn: {\n          \"from\": { opacity: \"0\" },\n          \"to\": { opacity: \"1\" }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n};\n</script>\n<style>\nbody {\n  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  min-height: max(884px, 100dvh);\n}\n.material-symbols-outlined {\n  font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;\n}\n.text-shadow-premium {\n  text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n}\n.no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-surface text-on-surface selection:bg-primary/30\">\n\n<!-- Navigation Bar -->\n<nav class=\"fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#0e0e0e]/60 backdrop-blur-xl transition-all\" aria-label=\"Navigation\">\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 h-12\">\n<!-- Logo Section -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-xl\" data-icon=\"apple\" aria-label=\"Apple Logo\">apple</span>\n<span class=\"font-semibold tracking-tight text-[0.875rem]\">iPhone 18 Pro Max</span>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Center Navigation Links -->\n<div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-8\">\n<a href=\"#overview\" class=\"text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold text-[0.875rem] hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity duration-200\">Overview</a>\n<a href=\"#tech-specs\" class=\"text-[#ababab] hover:text-[#e5e5e5] transition-colors duration-200 text-[0.875rem]\">Tech Specs</a>\n<a href=\"#compare\" class=\"text-[#ababab] hover:text-[#e5e5e5] transition-colors duration-200 text-[0.875rem]\">Compare</a>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Buy Button -->\n<div class=\"flex items-center\">\n<button class=\"bg-primary text-on-primary px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold hover:opacity-80 active:scale-95 duration-200 transition-all focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none\">\nBuy\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</nav>\n\n<main aria-label=\"Main Content\">\n\n<!-- Hero Section -->\n<section id=\"overview\" class=\"relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-24 pb-12 overflow-hidden bg-surface scroll-smooth\">\n<div class=\"z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl\">\n<h1 class=\"font-headline text-[3.5rem] md:text-[5rem] lg:text-[6.5rem] font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-6 opacity-0 animate-fadeIn\">\nTitanium.<br/>Groundbreaking.\n</h1>\n<p class=\"text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem] text-on-surface-variant font-medium tracking-tight mb-12\">\niPhone 18 Pro Max.\n</p>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6\">\n<button class=\"bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:bg-primary-dim transition-all active:scale-95 duration-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none\">\nBuy Now\n</button>\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"text-primary text-lg font-semibold hover:underline flex items-center gap-2 transition-all duration-200\">\nWatch the film <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-xl\">play_circle</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Hero Macro Asset -->\n<div class=\"mt-16 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto relative px-6\">\n<div class=\"aspect-[16/9] w-full bg-surface-container rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group\">\n<img alt=\"iPhone 18 Pro Max Titanium macro photography showing brushed obsidian texture\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-75 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000\" data-alt=\"Close-up macro photography of brushed obsidian titanium texture on a sleek smartphone frame with dramatic rim lighting and deep shadows\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDcijgOCSNOiLFwHRXmpPUwHoG4J8a6FRRbWEg4g78CkoLJ0EVxhi5g6Ae1U9WYwjXf2uEnPm-4Dntufzlkg-IWrUJg2GDKDEp3b_sOL9oqes2pT__2-oJ5Jz_8J_9SEofmAvCx2xcZXqyjd3LwwWACUgwb9Ca_gO0UE5MQGgCGcqyqwTfQG6x8xWtqvf5IARWi3LBvjKwdtYN8Kc220Hn3CaebqktriH9UXxvCuI-xA8nn24v6PveRMjBtUKI9h-cFJLYF-DatRVY2\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"/>\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-transparent to-transparent\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- Feature Bento Grid -->\n<section id=\"tech-specs\" class=\"py-32 px-6 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto scroll-smooth\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6\">\n\n<!-- A18 Pro Chip Card -->\n<div class=\"md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-10 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden group min-h-[500px]\">\n<div>\n<span class=\"text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase mb-4 block\">Engineered for Intelligence</span>\n<h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-on-surface leading-tight mb-4\">A18 Pro. The most efficient chip ever in a smartphone.</h2>\n<p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-md\">Our next-generation 2-nanometer architecture delivers 40% faster performance while consuming half the power.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"relative h-64 mt-8 flex items-center justify-center\">\n<div class=\"absolute w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[100px]\"></div>\n<div class=\"w-48 h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-container to-surface-container-high rounded-3xl border border-outline-variant/20 flex items-center justify-center shadow-inner relative z-10\">\n<span class=\"text-primary font-black text-4xl italic\">A18</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 100MP Camera System Card -->\n<div class=\"md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-10 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-hidden relative group min-h-[500px]\">\n<div class=\"z-10\">\n<h2 class=\"text-[2rem] font-bold text-on-surface leading-tight mb-4\">100MP Triple System.</h2>\n<p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-base\">Photonic Engine 3.0 captures detail unseen by the human eye.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-full h-auto group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700\">\n<img alt=\"Professional triple camera lens array with metallic rings and glass reflections\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover grayscale\" data-alt=\"Extreme close-up of a high-end triple camera lens array on the back of a black phone with metallic rings and deep glass reflections\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDiCL4Ws6teUFLNwZsTkJNQQ8Q7ukw5NgsYeYdIGti7_gu2a8YqVBhs6RlizOlrY6QLqBNae2ob1mKzMry6exVNPHKVdX4rtW-U2R-upJZkRi1iRFJA3eG8Eejx7c8HlhC0YFiaHgdtp9VptJt1_2KnyQw9LPAd0EwQ58bZiFyaJG30hlU9MufcuNS1tIzPL1SW9j3onpMS6p0uivda5lf7BhU7hz_64ocz5QV1V1cl86u9boMCbQKk-C_0HCTkSWXRo-pids205PAa\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Zero-Edge Display Card -->\n<div class=\"md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-high rounded-xl p-10 flex flex-col group min-h-[400px]\">\n<h2 class=\"text-[1.75rem] font-bold text-on-surface leading-tight mb-4\">Zero-Edge Display.</h2>\n<p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-base mb-8\">Ultra-narrow borders that disappear into the titanium frame. More screen, less everything else.</p>\n<div class=\"mt-auto bg-surface p-4 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/10 shadow-2xl\">\n<div class=\"h-1 w-24 bg-primary/20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4\"></div>\n<div class=\"aspect-[9/16] bg-surface-container rounded-md overflow-hidden relative\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-transparent\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Titanium Strength Card -->\n<div class=\"md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container rounded-xl p-10 flex items-center justify-between overflow-hidden relative group min-h-[400px]\">\n<div class=\"max-w-sm z-10\">\n<h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-on-surface leading-tight mb-4\">Grade 5 Titanium.</h2>\n<p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-lg\">Forged in heat, refined by light. Stronger than steel, lighter than ever.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 h-full w-1/2 overflow-hidden opacity-50\">\n<img alt=\"Raw forged titanium texture with industrial ripples and shadows\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-1000\" data-alt=\"Abstract metallic texture with raw forged titanium ripples and dark industrial shadows with cold blue highlights\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCU9xn3ZTBZRIE2lZvptikk8xcwZDQi4MbVEuv4tT90eNwTOo2jWvqjiHTy0g6mZ6U1UoHI34Xh7JOgV9BzPBWpmfrsO_TNMPtMucpuSRVqEyqnzh3fiaXs5-8_aeHls5a1Zn5_VqN56k2vz42Sc61kizT_1JA8L1MlbZZD8lLryxn3yjdnJ-lmDxGPw01_h2RaDDZrI2Kj2P3-RC1kGAq9uFoW_aK4H4OgRpeS-_KYpIckLT1tYkNUTd_OwKnrXmoEGFLN-3zmrjjl\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- Immersive Hardware Showcase -->\n<section class=\"bg-surface-container-lowest py-32 overflow-hidden scroll-smooth\">\n<div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col items-center\">\n<div class=\"text-center mb-20\">\n<h2 class=\"text-[3rem] md:text-[4.5rem] font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-6\">Designed for the extraordinary.</h2>\n<p class=\"text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto\">From the textured matte glass to the precision-machined buttons, every detail has been obsessively reconsidered.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-full relative h-[600px] flex items-center justify-center\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none opacity-20\">\n<span class=\"text-[15rem] font-black text-surface-container tracking-tighter select-none\">PRO MAX</span>\n</div>\n<img alt=\"iPhone 18 Pro side profile with titanium frame and precision buttons\" class=\"max-w-full h-auto max-h-[500px] object-contain drop-shadow-[0_35px_35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)] z-10\" data-alt=\"Side profile view of a slim black titanium smartphone showing the volume buttons and mute switch with sharp professional studio lighting\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAy_mQwBZseerTlyjc2FJXSTaEG3L8faUR8YYZ-z2gFSAR-H53TcFYABhurCDy6sZPdLWij7d7sUnTQI-tbI1G6oxL6ToDB7Js29QS2iPHNZDbANvJ8EyEceWdS0tvkJ94jqw9QVqgzC4ycvTPrT-Dau2zVApS7DSbFnvb6eWDzoamA_G26va_K-Mre3Si99mx0ZqCNjh7mGwinQhuhXaRQAmLcvF2L_GNcqA1M6A_P3r1qPkRmwmCcqe_Wh8HChNBV65aAaKcwSdlx\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- CTA Section -->\n<section id=\"compare\" class=\"py-32 bg-surface text-center scroll-smooth\">\n<div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6\">\n<h2 class=\"text-[2.5rem] md:text-[4rem] font-bold text-on-surface mb-8\">Titanium strength. Pro performance.</h2>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4\">\n<button class=\"w-full md:w-auto bg-primary text-on-primary px-12 py-5 rounded-full text-xl font-bold hover:bg-primary-dim transition-all active:scale-95 duration-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none\">\nOrder Now\n</button>\n<button class=\"w-full md:w-auto bg-surface-container text-on-surface px-12 py-5 rounded-full text-xl font-bold border border-outline-variant/10 hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all active:scale-95 duration-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:outline-none\">\nCompare Models\n</button>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-8 text-on-surface-variant\">From $1199 or $49.95/mo. for 24 mo.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</main>\n\n<!-- Footer -->\n<footer class=\"bg-[#131313] w-full py-12 px-6 border-t border-[#484848]/15\" role=\"contentinfo\">\n<div class=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-7 gap-8 mb-12\">\n\n<!-- Store Column -->\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold text-[0.75rem]\">Store</span>\n<ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Mac</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">iPad</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">iPhone</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Watch</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Entertainment Column -->\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold text-[0.75rem]\">Entertainment</span>\n<ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Apple One</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Apple TV+</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Apple Music</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Apple Arcade</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Support Column -->\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\">\n<span class=\"text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold text-[0.75rem]\">Support</span>\n<ul class=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">iPhone Support</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Apple Care</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Community</li>\n<li class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Contact Us</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<!-- About Column -->\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 lg:col-span-4\">\n<span class=\"text-[#e5e5e5] font-bold text-[0.75rem]\">About Apple</span>\n<p class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed\">Shop at Apple Store, call 1-800-MY-APPLE, or find a reseller. iPhone 18 Pro Max is available in select markets starting Oct 2024.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- Footer Bottom -->\n<div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-[#484848]/15 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4\">\n<p class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed\">Copyright © 2024 Apple Inc. All rights reserved.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-6\">\n<span class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Privacy Policy</span>\n<span class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Terms of Use</span>\n<span class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Sales Policy</span>\n<span class=\"text-[#ababab] text-[0.75rem] leading-relaxed hover:underline cursor-pointer\">Legal</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</footer>\n\n<script>\n// Smooth scroll behavior for anchor links\ndocument.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n  anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n    const href = this.getAttribute('href');\n    if (href !== 'javascript:void(0)' && href !== '#') {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      const target = document.querySelector(href);\n      if (target) {\n        target.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });\n      }\n    }\n  });\n});\n\n// Button click handlers for CTAs\ndocument.querySelectorAll('button').forEach(button => {\n  button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    // Visual feedback - scale animation already handled by CSS active:scale-95\n  });\n});\n</script>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
